wiki.content:
"Thank You" peaked at #1 on the U.S. Hot Dance Club Play Chart and the U.S. Adult Contemporary Chart in the Summer of 2001.
 
 The song was famously sampled in Eminem's 2000 landmark single "Stan." She also appeared in the video for the song.
